rComments: Good course and the prof is good too. She's full of life and expresses love for what she teaches. However, I could take three psychology courses (known to have intense heavy readings) in place of one of her courses and have the exact same workload. plus text has too many statistics, but her lecs are interesting. I wish there were fewer readings.

Definitely a cool prof! very hippie-ish. she talks very quickly  - but if you have a laptop and can type her major points - she covers a lot of the text. this is my second course with her and i really enjoy her classes ... currently doing quite well

This is a really interesting course. The prof is very kind and friendly. She is very knowledgable about the subject and seems easy to talk to. My only complaint is the heavy readings. I think it's too much for one course. But, she is such a kind and wonderful prof. She is very smart and I feel privileged to be taught by her.
